  <div class="field-body">
     <p>We have a plan to disseminate the surveilance techniques used by the NSA publicly to as many people as possible. Rather than letting the NSA hide behind a wall of silence, let's show the world what it really means to be inside the PRISM!</p>
   </div>
  <h3 class="field-label">
    Brief (internal) description  </h3>

  <div class="field-brief-internal-description">
    The plan is to actually suck people's data from their facebook and twitter accounts using droid-sheep or some other means, and post sweet messages from the NSA to their pages.  We want to get a bunch of people working on this simultaneously across the country.  </div>
